  =====================================================
  install gems:
    $ bundle install
    
  start sinatra application on localhost:
    $ rackup config.rb

  deploy sinatra project on heroku:
<% if !gitinit then %>
    $ git init
      [do your work...]
<% end %>
    $ heroku create <%= name %>
    $ git push heroku master
    $ heroku open
  ======================================================
